What's going on, girl?

05:47.556 --> 05:48.887
- Look.
- What happened?

05:48.974 --> 05:50.681
They shut the place down, Cheryl.

05:50.767 --> 05:52.303
They said they moved
the plant to Mexico.

05:52.394 --> 05:54.476
- Hurry!
- And they didn't tell us!

05:54.563 --> 05:56.645
- Move move!
- Go go! Come on!

05:56.732 --> 05:59.690
Wait! We were supposed
to get paid today!

06:01.903 --> 06:04.861
- I've got to pay my light bill today.
- Who has a match?!

06:04.948 --> 06:08.782
I'm going to burn this place down!
Who has a match?!

06:08.869 --> 06:11.031
Don't give this fool
no match. She bipolar.

06:11.121 --> 06:13.954
