You smoke, Georgia!

06:17.169 --> 06:19.160
Give me a match.
Give it to me.

06:26.553 --> 06:28.794
Cheryl, put that out.

06:30.307 --> 06:32.173
Come on, I'm trying
to chill out.

06:32.267 --> 06:34.349
You know with your
chemical imbalance

06:34.436 --> 06:36.143
