after she wakes up and eats.

07:35.914 --> 07:38.451
- Okay.
- The child is sleeping.

07:40.335 --> 07:41.837
Thank you, Miss Mildred!

07:41.920 --> 07:45.003
- She's crazy.
- Naw, she's all right.

07:45.090 --> 07:48.208
Shoot. I don't know what
I'm gonna do now though.

07:48.301 --> 07:51.089
- She don't play with her money.
- Yeah, me neither.

07:51.179 --> 07:53.637
