25:13.304 --> 25:16.842
He had a-- he was there
and everything. I miss my daddy.

25:16.932 --> 25:18.468
It's going to be
all right, Mr. Brown.

25:18.559 --> 25:20.220
I just can't take it.
Lord, take the wheel.

25:20.311 --> 25:21.893
