25:23.898 --> 25:27.061
- Chicago's a nice town.
- Yeah, I like it.

25:27.151 --> 25:29.392
- Mm-hmm.
- See, she likes it.

25:29.486 --> 25:31.978
- I couldn't live there.
- Would you look at the road?

25:32.072 --> 25:35.030
Huh-uh, gimme the South.
Yes, I like the trees of the South.

25:35.117 --> 25:38.485
I don't like it. There's too much
smog and stuff there.

25:38.579 --> 25:40.320
- Yeah?
- My daddy liked it though.

25:40.414 --> 25:43.156
- It's okay, Mr. Brown.
- He was always in Chicago.

25:43.250 --> 25:45.457
It's all right. I want you
to watch the road.

25:45.544 --> 25:47.455
Oh wait, now watch the road!

25:47.546 --> 25:50.004
He just taught me so much.

25:50.090 --> 25:51.831
He taught me how
to dance and swim.

25:51.926 --> 25:54.213
Imiss him.

25:59.767 --> 26:02.850
