26:13.781 --> 26:17.524
- Well, my mama--
- Where is everybody? Oh!

26:17.618 --> 26:19.609
- Here we go.
- Y'all Daddy go.

26:19.703 --> 26:21.785
Oh, Lord, help me.
Help me.

26:21.872 --> 26:25.035
Vera, will you get somewhere
and sit down without all that drama?

26:25.125 --> 26:27.207
Go on, y'all, daddy dead!

26:27.294 --> 26:29.251
Vera, get ahold
of yourself now.

26:29.338 --> 26:32.376
Oh, Lord, oh, Lord, I just don't know
what I'm gonna do, y'all.

26:32.466 --> 26:34.457
