28:02.556 --> 28:05.093
- Vera's son.
- Hello.

28:05.184 --> 28:07.141
Who are you?
Now wait-- hey hey hey!

28:07.227 --> 28:09.639
Hey, Brown,
this your daughter too?

28:11.690 --> 28:13.647
I'm Brenda
and this is Michael,

28:13.734 --> 28:15.771
Lena and Tosha.

28:15.861 --> 28:17.818
