for the funeral.

28:17.905 --> 28:20.567
- Where'd she come from?
- Chicago.

28:20.657 --> 28:24.241
Daddy! Daddy!

28:24.328 --> 28:27.571
- Okay, Ma.
- My daddy lived in Chicago long ago.

28:27.664 --> 28:29.496
Help me, Jesus!

28:29.583 --> 28:32.701
Come on, y'all. I'm gonna show you
