28:32.795 --> 28:35.503
- Oh, thank you.
- Just go on up the stairs

28:35.589 --> 28:38.126
- and turn to your left.
- See you later.

28:38.217 --> 28:39.673
- Good night.
- Mm-hmm.

28:39.760 --> 28:43.594
And, Vera, you all can sleep
in Pop Brown's old room.

28:43.680 --> 28:47.844
Oh, now I ain't sleeping in some room
some dead man died in.

28:47.935 --> 28:51.053
