29:14.962 --> 29:18.171
Oh yes, that's Harry.

29:18.257 --> 29:21.375
Yo, hey, Harry!

29:21.468 --> 29:23.300
- Hey, Mr. Brown.
- You doing all right?

29:23.387 --> 29:24.673
- Yeah.
- Yeah yeah yeah.

29:24.763 --> 29:26.504
