29:38.902 --> 29:40.404
Just came by to pay
my condolences.

29:40.487 --> 29:42.319
Oh, you ain't got to pay
for nothing.

29:42.406 --> 29:44.147
We got $25,
everything is covered.

29:44.241 --> 29:47.074
Yeah, Daddy left a big insurance
policy for that much.

29:47.161 --> 29:49.118
Hey, Mike, I was watching you
from upstairs.

29:49.204 --> 29:50.740
